headline: Morgan Stanley Australia CEO on Business Outlook
summary: Richard Wagner, CEO of Morgan Stanley Australia, discusses his outlook and growth strategy for the business, as he sees an uptick in M&A and IPO activity in the Australian market in the second half of 2025. He speaks exclusively with Haidi Stroud Watts on the sidelines of the annual Morgan Stanley Australia Summit on "Bloomberg: The Asia Trade".
